items.title: Lawrie Conole
items.content_text: Lawrie Conole has over 40 years of ecological experience in Victoria and Australia, and parts of Asia. His background includes state and local government and university research roles, as well as ecological consulting in small to multinational companies.

items.title: Mark Ridgway
items.content_text:
Amateur field naturalist fascinated by all life forms and particularly evolved inter-relationships. 
Recent years focusing more on moths, fungi, wasps, flies.
